Comment: 0,0:27:56.32,0:27:56.36,op jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.32,0:28:01.78,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs55}This is a fate that brought us here watch my long shot
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.79,0:28:12.33,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs55}Feel like I am falling into the flame of lies
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.33,0:28:15.00,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs55}Tell me what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.75,0:28:19.38,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs55}Trying not to step back to where I used to belong
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.38,0:28:22.26,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs55}Looking for the escape from pain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.59,0:28:26.64,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs55}I will cross my fingers hoping not to be sacrificed
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.64,0:28:30.10,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs55}約束したんだ君とその希望に
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.10,0:28:33.85,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs55}Get in the raid Get ready for the time to come
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.85,0:28:37.40,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs55}浮かび上がるシルエット追いかけ
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.40,0:28:40.74,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs55}Drop down the reason why I'm standing here alone
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.74,0:28:44.32,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs55}May be it's already too late to regain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.53,0:28:49.70,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs55}運命としてかかげた灯を失くさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.70,0:28:51.00,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs55}Ever again
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.00,0:28:54.50,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs55}What if I could right my wrongs and save you from the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.50,0:28:56.25,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs55}It's not enough
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.25,0:29:03.97,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs55}It's not enough for me to break the rule upon this world
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.05,0:29:09.01,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs55}I will never gonna leave you never wanna lose you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.01,0:29:11.35,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs55}we'll make it in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.64,0:29:17.65,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs55}Not backing down for real I won't trace someone else's life
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.11,0:29:20.03,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs55}I know who I am
Comment: 0,0:35:07.79,0:35:07.79,op ch,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.32,0:28:01.78,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs52}命运将我们引领至此 并看着我跳战不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.79,0:28:12.33,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs52}感觉我堕入了谎言的火焰中
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.33,0:28:15.00,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs52}说出你对我的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.75,0:28:19.38,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs52}尽力不去走回头路
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.38,0:28:22.26,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs52}探求走出痛苦的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.59,0:28:26.64,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs52}我合十双手去祈求不必牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.64,0:28:30.10,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs52}这是我和你的希望所订下的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.10,0:28:33.85,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs52}在时机成熟前做好出击的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.85,0:28:37.40,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs52}去追赶那个浮现出来的黑影
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.40,0:28:40.74,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs52}放弃那个让我单独一人的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.74,0:28:44.32,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs52}或许这已经太迟
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.53,0:28:49.70,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs52}不要舍去作为命运的那道光
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.70,0:28:51.00,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs52}没有下次
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.00,0:28:54.50,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs52}若我能修补错误并将你救出苦海
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.50,0:28:56.25,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs52}这并不足以
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.25,0:29:03.97,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs52}并不足以让我打破这世界的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.05,0:29:09.01,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs52}我绝不离开你 绝不想失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.01,0:29:11.35,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs52}我们来结束这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.64,0:29:17.65,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs52}别再退缩 这辈子我不会跟随别人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.11,0:29:20.03,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs52}我知道自己是谁
Comment: 0,0:27:30.04,0:27:30.08,ed jp,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:27:36.86,0:27:46.63,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}壊れないように優しく抱いて　溶けて涙流す
Comment: 0,0:27:47.20,0:27:57.83,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}そんな氷の人形みたいに なれないから
Comment: 0,0:28:02.26,0:28:12.06,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}もう逃げない　知りたいの　強く
Comment: 0,0:28:12.06,0:28:13.76,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}―I believe…believe in you―
Comment: 0,0:28:13.76,0:28:17.86,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}きっと一番の約束の言葉
Comment: 0,0:28:17.86,0:28:22.26,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}痛いくらい握って離さない
Comment: 0,0:28:22.56,0:28:28.20,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}わがままな今連れて　誰のものでもない未来を
Comment: 0,0:28:28.20,0:28:30.90,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}そこから始めるの
Comment: 0,0:28:30.90,0:28:41.46,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}空を掴む(夢の欠片)　祈りの手を(指先まで)
Comment: 0,0:28:41.46,0:28:46.53,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}伸ばすかぎり(生けるかぎり)
Comment: 0,0:28:46.53,0:28:54.60,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}そこに本当はあるの
Comment: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:20.52,ed ch,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:27:36.86,0:27:46.63,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}小心翼翼地温柔抱着 使它流下熔化的眼泪
Comment: 0,0:27:47.20,0:27:57.83,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}我可没法成为那样的冰雪人偶
Comment: 0,0:28:02.26,0:28:12.06,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}我再也不会逃避 我想要知道变强的方法
Comment: 0,0:28:12.06,0:28:13.76,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}
Comment: 0,0:28:13.76,0:28:17.86,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}将第一个约定的话语
Comment: 0,0:28:17.86,0:28:22.26,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}紧握到疼痛 绝不放开
Comment: 0,0:28:22.56,0:28:28.20,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}带着任性的现在 前往不属于任何人的未来
Comment: 0,0:28:28.20,0:28:30.90,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}从那里开始吧
Comment: 0,0:28:30.90,0:28:41.46,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}抓紧天空(梦想的碎片) 祈愿的手(直到指尖)
Comment: 0,0:28:41.46,0:28:46.53,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}只要还能够伸出(只要仍活着)
Comment: 0,0:28:46.53,0:28:54.60,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}那里就会有真物在
